&lt;p>We believe in making our simple but strong visual iconography open and accessible to all. We have assembled and designed these icons for use with the Community Health Toolkit based on human centered design principles.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>About the Icon Library&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="about-the-icon-library">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#about-the-icon-library" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;img alt="Example Icons" style="border-width:0" src="https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5bd25eea65a707ad54c1e8ca/t/5bf4a3442b6a2841cd402a05/1542759243884/CHT-feature-overview-01.png?format=1000w" />
